abstract: Britain's Prince Harry will be coming to Gila Bend, Arizona, for two months of military training, and the town's 2,000 residents are very eager to make his acquaintance.
snippet: The 2,000 residents of an Arizona town are eager for the arrival of Britain’s Prince Harry, who will spend two months there for training — and perhaps a shrimp-eating contest.
lead_paragraph: The 2,000 residents of an Arizona town are eager for the arrival of Britain’s Prince Harry, who will spend two months there for training — and perhaps a shrimp-eating contest.
